<subSubSection box="[199,978,473,498]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="34.[151,1436,151,748]" box="[199,978,473,498]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">
<emphasis box="[199,553,473,498]" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,327,473,498]" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Etymology.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Luk &amp; Marshall" authorityYear="2014" box="[335,553,473,497]" class="Insecta" family="Sphaeroceridae" genus="Aptilotella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gloriosa">Aptilotella gloriosa</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
is named for its splendid colouration.
</paragraph>
